00:14:09.150 --> 00:14:12.170
I think we're just all working
together, but believe me,

00:14:12.170 --> 00:14:17.170
it's a privilege for me to work
with Emilie, and David, and Danny,

00:14:17.170 --> 00:14:22.880
and Anthony, who I also knew
when he was much younger

00:14:22.880 --> 00:14:25.630
and it keeps you on your toes.

00:14:25.630 --> 00:14:30.610
I mean, I have to play my
best to play with these guys

00:14:30.610 --> 00:14:33.760 position:56%
and it's -- it's really a privilege.

00:14:33.760 --> 00:14:38.320
&gt;&gt; Anne E. McLean: I think another
thing that you guys always touch

00:14:38.320 --> 00:14:42.920
