the place, I'm not at Marlboro.

00:32:35.130 --> 00:32:36.690
That's the only comment I have.

00:32:36.690 --> 00:32:37.990
There's --

00:32:37.990 --> 00:32:40.430
&gt;&gt; Anne E. McLean: It's
a time honored tradition.

00:32:40.430 --> 00:32:44.800
All -- all ages, all backgrounds,
all instruments apparently,

00:32:44.800 --> 00:32:48.080
you know, even Mr. Serkin.

00:32:48.080 --> 00:32:49.600
&gt;&gt; David McCarroll: Yeah, no it
really -- really does happen.

00:32:49.600 --> 00:32:55.310
